    <item>
      <title>美国经济在选举前放缓但稳健</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-economy-slowing-but-solid-near-election-unemployment-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统大选前夕，最近的数据显示，获胜者将继承一个蓬勃发展的经济，这得益于美国消费者尽管多年来物价和利率居高不下，但仍坚持消费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-economy-slowing-but-solid-near-election-unemployment-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:49:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克未能将选民抽奖案件提交美国法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/musk-loses-bid-to-send-philadelphia-sweepstakes-case-to-us-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）未能将一项针对他每天向选民赠送百万美元的奖金的诉讼移交联邦法院，而这起诉讼由费城进步派地方检察官提起，并再次交由州法院法官审理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/musk-loses-bid-to-send-philadelphia-sweepstakes-case-to-us-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
